If an error page (stack trace) is shown, we should provide a button that will create a support request on support.atlassian.com with the contents of the page and the user details. This could be done via email or XML-RPC.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-4863].
