From https://support.atlassian.com/browse/CSP-1784:

"We only use the date of the blog post and generally write pretty meaningless titles. Can the {blog-posts} macro be configured to only show the post itself and not the title (which comes in a pretty large heading)."

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
